    "bio": "Full-stack automation expert combining n8n, frontend & backend development, and hard-coded solutions to build powerful, scalable workflows. Skilled in data parsing (PDF/Excel), API integrations (banking, property, financial), email systems, and real-time sync. I create custom dashboards, API layers, and advanced automations that go beyond “no-code,” ",
